modDescription:
Simple little thing to stop the tree falling animation. Nothing fancy but may help if you play 7 Days to Die on a toaster. Mmmm jam. Or just hate [trees](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-trees/) having a final revenge attempt. Should work on all trees, even new/modded ones.
